item.title: Re: for the TOTE - sick of him sp.mission
item.content:encoded:
To bingo any ninja, your village must have a spy in the village that ninja is in.

If you can't find the ninja the page where you select a bingo target: go to the ninja's player lookup, look at what village they are in, and try to get a spy into that village. Once that is done, you should be able to see them in your bingo book.
